      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Jan 31 obituary of Bernie Friedkin</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary in some copies yesterday about Bernie Friedkin, a boxer from Brooklyn who was known as Schoolboy, missated his height and the place of residence of a surviving granddaughter, Sabrina Saltz, who announced the death. Mr. Friedkin was 5 feet 6 inches, not 5 feet 3 inches; and Ms. Saltz lives in Staten Island, not Brooklyn. An updated obituary appears today on Page B8.</p>
      </block>
